sub_title: Recht door zee mediator bij Recht door zee mediation
summary:
Eversince working as an Interior Designer for television I have broadened my capacities. 
I don't have a signature when it comes to designing an interior | exterior. I talk to the owners, listen to their wishes and translate that into a formfitted design. 
Working for television has taught me to take a design tot the next level and take one step further. Th√°t is what makes a design different and unique. 
My motto: Because class never goes out of style


When it comes to the High Heel Workout, that is something I do from personal experience. Walking in high heels since I was 15, I'm well-trained. Combining that with the sporting-experience of Eline, we have a solid base for a great Workout. Our goal is to get so many requests for workouts, that we have to train other girls, so they can give the workout. 
Eline en I would still be the ones developing the workouts furthermore and giving it when we decide to. Also the PR and Marketing would stay in our hands.

Specialties: Creating wonderfull designs for interiors | exteriors, taking that one step beyond. 

Making walking on high heels an elegant, sexy and fun experience for everyone.
